==Overview==
[[Employee]]s gain experience in [[skill]]s as they preform tasks related to those skills.

The amount of experience required for each level is not shown in game, but a percentage of completion towards the next skill level can be seen by hovering over the relevant skill icon in the employee interface.

==Factors==
Experience gain is based on the time spent doing the task.

